            "content": "Bottom Line for Gladden Farms Homeowners: When your furnace is 10+ years old and facing repairs over $800, strongly consider replacement. Modern high-efficiency systems deliver substantial energy savings, improved comfort for two-story floor plans, and better performance in Gladden Farms desert climate. Our honest technicians will provide detailed cost analysis comparing repair vs. replacement with 10-year total cost of ownership specific to your home. We never pressure replacement—we provide facts and let you decide. Explore our [link:/services/heating-marana|Marana heating services] and [link:/services/heating-oro-valley|Oro Valley heating services] for nearby northwest Tucson communities."
